<H3> <TI>   Poll on Governor, Renowned Legislative Councilors </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Poll on Governor, Renowned Legislative Councilors </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94CM0266B Hong Kong TANGTAI [CONTEMPORARY] in Chinese No 35, 
15 Feb 94 pp 6-7 </F>

<F P=103> 94CM0266B </F>
<F P=104>  Hong Kong TANGTAI [CONTEMPORARY] </F>
