<TEXT>
CSO 

  [Summary] At the end of March, rural saving deposits in 
Zhejiang Province exceeded 38 billion yuan, an increase of 5.8 
billion yuan over the beginning of the year. By the end of 
March, agricultural banks and credit cooperatives in Zhejiang 
allocated 4.834 billion yuan in loans for spring planting, an 
11.5 percent increase over the same period in 1993. 

