<H3> <TI>   Mobile Neutron Radiography System Certified </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Mobile Neutron Radiography System Certified </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94P60247C Beijing RENMIN RIBAO OVERSEAS EDITION in Chinese 
14 Apr 94 p 3 </F>

<F P=103> 94P60247C </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing RENMIN RIBAO OVERSEAS EDITION </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
