<H3> <TI>   70 Achievements of MEI Institute 13 Certified </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    70 Achievements of MEI Institute 13 Certified </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94P60227B Beijing DIANZI XUEBAO [ACTA ELECTRONICA SINICA] in 
Chinese Vol 22 No 2, Feb 94 p 34 </F>

<F P=103> 94P60227B </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing DIANZI XUEBAO [ACTA ELECTRONICA SINICA] </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


