<H4>    MPT Building Public Digital Data Network </H4>

<F P=102> 94P60236C Beijing ZHONGGUO DIANZI BAO [CHINA ELECTRONICS 
NEWS] in Chinese 21 Mar 94 p 3 </F>

<F P=103> 94P60236C </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing ZHONGGUO DIANZI BAO [CHINA ELECTRONICS 
