<H4>    SSTC Chief Engineer Urges Developing Infrastructure </H4>

<F P=102> 94P60236E Beijing KEJI RIBAO [SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY DAILY] 
in Chinese 1 Apr 94 p 1 </F>

<F P=103> 94P60236E </F>
