<H4>    Shanghai Firm Completes Satellite Network </H4>

<F P=102> 94P60236F Shanghai WEN HUI BAO in Chinese 4 Apr 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 94P60236F </F>
<F P=104>  Shanghai WEN HUI BAO </F>
