<H4>    SIC Official Urges State, Industry to Build Infrastructure </H4>

<F P=102> 94P60236H Beijing KEJI RIBAO [SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY DAILY] 
in Chinese 16 Apr 94 p 1 </F>

<F P=103> 94P60236H </F>
