<H3> <TI>   End-Office Digital SPC Switch Developed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    End-Office Digital SPC Switch Developed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94P60252B Beijing KEJI RIBAO [SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY DAILY] 
in Chinese 7 Apr 94 p 1 </F>

<F P=103> 94P60252B </F>
